												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/alejandroheredia/">Alejandro Heredia</a></h6>
													Alejandro Heredia is a writer from the Bronx. He has received fellowships from LAMBDA Literary, Dominican Studies Institute, UNLV’s Black Mountain Institute, and elsewhere. He received an MFA in fiction from Hunter College. <em>Loca</em> is his debut novel.																									</div>
